  "steps": [
    "Prepare glucose detection reagent mix by adding: Luciferin Detection Solution Reductase Reductase Substrate Glucose Dehydrogenase NAD These reagents are part of a boxed set - Promega&#39;s Glucose-Glo Assay.",
    "Dilute 2 µL overnight culture in 198 µL 1x PBS and mix",
    "Aliquot 50 µL of each sample into three wells of 96-well plate to create triplicates",
    "Add 50 µL of glucose detection reagent mix into each well",
    "Include PBS-only wells as blank"
